data.description: Private, accessible, Hill Top home, located on +/-17 acres. Enjoy Hill Country living in this beautiful, 4 bedroom 3 bath, custom home, with Brazilian mesquite floors, instant hot water, 3 walk in attics and too many extras to name. (See additional info.) This horse ready property has: 2- 12' x12' stalls (room to add), tack room, hay shed, one set of permanent pens & one set of portable pens. Work shop can be converted to guest house, toilet and shower in place. Storage on carport.
data.whatILove:
Secluded, on a private road, without road noise, with easy access to Kerrville, Fredericksburg, Boerne and San Antonio. Hunting allowed. Enjoy your morning cup of coffee off the porch while watching the deer browse around the feeder.
This home is economical to run, some of its great features: 
Custom Limestone Rock and Hardiplank Exterior siding
6" insulation on North wall, radiant barrier, blown-in High-R Value insulation. (exterior walls)
Brazilian Mesquite Hardwood and ceramic floors throughout
Custom Hickory kitchen cabinets
Cast Marble Counter-tops, showers and tub
8 Leaded Glass windows
Stand and Seam roof on home other buildings are metal
4-ring water storage tank, with 2" Fire-hose connection
Culligan Water softener (owned)
Marathon Lifetime Water heater with hot water circulatory system
Whole house fan
Walk in Attics
 Just to list a few..........
